<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَعِيدًا عَنِ الْمَنهِيِّ مُجْتَنِبًا لَهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>حَرِيصًا عَلَى الْمَأْمُورِ فِي الْعُسْرِ وَالْيُسْرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِنْ رُمْتَ أَنْ تَحْظَى بِقَلْبٍ مُنَوَّرٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نَقِيٍّ مِنَ الأَغْيَارِ فَاعْكُفْ عَلَيَّ الذِّكْرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَوَاظِبْ عَلَيْهِ فِي الظَّلامِ وَفِي الضِّيَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَفِي كُلِّ حَالٍ بِاللِّسَانِ وَبِالسِّرِّ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَصَفِّ مِنْ الأَكْدَارِ سِرَّكَ إِنَّهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِذَا مَا صَفَا أَوْلاكَ مَعْنَى مِنَ الْفِكْرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَبِالْجِدِّ وَالصَّبْرِ الْجَمِيلِ تَحِلُّ فِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَسِيحِ الْعُلى فَاِسْتَوْصِ بِالْجِدِّ وَالصَّبْرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَكُنْ شَاكِرًا للهِ قَلْبًا وَقالِبًا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَلَى فَضْلِهِ إِنَّ الْمَزِيدَ مَعَ الشُّكْرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>تَوَكَلَّ عَلَى مَوْلاكَ وَاِرْضَ بِحُكْمِهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَكُنْ مُخْلِصًا للهِ فِي السِّرِّ وَالْجَهْرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>قَنُوعًا بِمَا أَعْطَاكَ مُسْتَغْنِيًا بِهِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>لَهُ حَامِدًا فِي حَالِيْ الْعُسْرِ وَالْيُسْرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَكُنْ بَاذِلاً لِلْفَضْلِ سَمْحًا وَلا تَخَفْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مِنَ اللهِ إِقْتَارًا وَلا تَخْشَ مِنْ فَقْرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَإِيَّاكَ وَالدُّنْيَا فَإنَّ حَلالَهَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>حِسَابٌ وَفِي مَحْظُورِهَا الْهَتْكُ لِلسِّرِّ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>